what is CI & CD 
	Practice of building the code (binary code) periodically is known as CI.
	Created binary code can be deployed automatically is known as CD 
Continuous deployment or delivery.

Flow of the Jenkins process:
    dev write their code and commit it git ----Jenkins dev pipeline trigger 
	to compile, Unit test , code quality and security authentication check  on code.
    if everything is success then code merge to master branch.
	Now Jenkins pipeline trigger to compile, Unit test, check code quality & venerability.
once success the code upload to the artifactory.
