Sonar qube configuration?
	mvn clean install sonar:sonar
			or
stage('SonarQube analysis') {
    withSonarQubeEnv( credentialsId: 'f507a', installationName: 'My SonarQube Server') 
	{ // Will pick the global server connection you have configured
      sh './gradlew sonarqube'
    }

life cycle of maven?
validate - validate all necessary project information is available or not 
compile - compile the source code of the project
test - unit testing of compiled source code.
package - take the compiled code and package it as a JAR.
verify - run integration tests to ensure quality criteria are met.
install - install the package into the local repository, for use as a dependency in other projects locally
deploy - done in the build environment, copies the final package to the remote repository.
how to skip the test case in maven?
	mvn install -DskipTests
where i will write the webserver detail in maven?
	pom. xml 
how you are pushing package to jfrog? when you push which type artifactory it will land?

	curl -X PUT -u user_Id:password -T Maven-Upload-1.1.jar "http://url"
	
	or  in pom.xml 
		<pluginRepository>
			<id>Maven-Artifactory-Plugin</id>
			<url>https://jcenter.bintray.com</url>
		</pluginRepository>
	or   Jenkins Artifactory plugin  for jfrog can use 
	
	
